Thanks.

30
00:01:45,920 --> 00:01:47,285
It's a secret recipe.

31
00:01:47,820 --> 00:01:48,520
Military.

32
00:01:48,820 --> 00:01:50,575
[Mother:]
Oh a secret, uh.

33
00:01:51,820 --> 00:01:54,819
[Jerry:]  I can tell it
but, then I have to kill you.

34
00:01:54,820 --> 00:01:56,819
[Mother: LAUGHING]
Oh, I'm scared.

35
00:01:56,820 --> 00:01:58,819
[William:]  I'm going
to my room now.

36
